# mbsync (isync) 템플릿 — 보존용 읽기 전용 미러 (선택).
# 실행:  mbsync -c <this> -a       /  비번은 PassCmd 가 age 에서 읽음(평문 없음).
# 안전: Sync Pull + Expunge None → 원격에 절대 쓰지 않음(원격→로컬 복사만).

IMAPAccount example
Host imap.gmail.com
User you@example.com
PassCmd "mail-secret himalaya-example-imap"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore example-remote
Account example

MaildirStore example-local
Path /path/to/archive/example/
Inbox /path/to/archive/example/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel example
Far :example-remote:
Near :example-local:
Patterns "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Near
Sync Pull
Expunge None
SyncState *
